       Marine was soaked and steaming from the Acid shot out by Iron Raptor. 
But it had all been worth it. She was grounded, and now it was time to 
deliver the finalt blow.
       Marine thrust his sowrd level with her sizzled neck cord. He realized, 
however, that he would more than likely get electricuted or something. It 
didnt matter, if he had to die to take the fems life, he would do it.
       Ominous Prime and Quasar were knocked over by her tail. They scrambled 
up, weapons targeting her beaten backside. Once agian, they fired 12 shots a 
peice.
       Jackle gave a little giggle and sent 15 more shots from his plasma 
riffle wizzing at the fallen heroine.

       Hell Beast was pummled by Magnus, but Tankkpr sent 10 missles back at 
the brute while Rampage rolled away from Proto....who seems to all of a 
sudden appear out of thin air...kinda of odd and seems to borderline mode.
